headline: Johnson & Johnson Teams Up with Naomi Watts to Reveal Why an Eye Exam is the Ultimate Self-Care Move for Women Over 40
summary: Johnson & Johnson (NYSE: JNJ) – Johnson & Johnson, a global leader in eye health, has partnered with Academy Award–nominated actress, producer, and entrepreneur, Naomi Watts, to change the conversation about vision. Together, they'll encourage simple, practical steps—such as routine eye checks and reframing eye care as part of holistic healthy aging, so that it becomes an easy and empowering part of daily self-care.
